{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-tsx","path":"/数据结构-数组、链表、跳表基本实现和特性/数据结构-数组、链表、跳表基本实现和特性/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Orainsink's blog"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"703fa513-7e7b-5331-8950-5882502d30a2","excerpt":"数组(Array) 可直接访问数组元素, 直接访问的时间复杂度为 O(1) 删除指定项的过程: 移除指定项的数据 -> 将后续数组项向前平挪一个角标 -> 删除数组最后一项或者直接将数组的长度减一 添加指定项的过程: 在指定角标处插入添加的项 -> 后续数组项往后平挪一位 数组的添加和删除, 都是 O(n…","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/#%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84array\">数组(Array)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/#%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8linked-list\">链表(Linked-list)</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84-%E6%95%B0%E7%BB%84%E3%80%81%E9%93%BE%E8%A1%A8%E3%80%81%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E5%92%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%80%A7/#%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8\">跳表</a></li>\n</ul>","html":"<h2>数组(Array)</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>可直接访问数组元素, 直接访问的时间复杂度为 O(1)</li>\n<li>\n<p>删除指定项的过程:</p>\n<p>移除指定项的数据 -> 将后续数组项向前平挪一个角标 -> 删除数组最后一项或者直接将数组的长度减一</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>添加指定项的过程:</p>\n<p>在指定角标处插入添加的项 -> 后续数组项往后平挪一位</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>数组的添加和删除, 都是 O(n)的时间复杂度, 频繁的添加删除操作效率并不高.</p>\n<h2>链表(Linked-list)</h2>\n<p>js 实现 Node 类</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre style=\"counter-reset: linenumber NaN\" class=\"language-js line-numbers\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Node</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">val</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// 当前节点的值</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>val <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> val<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// next 指针, 指向下一个节点</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>next <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\" style=\"white-space: normal; width: auto; left: 0;\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></pre></div>\n<p>根据指针的差别, 链表又分为单向链表, 双向链表和循环链表</p>\n<p>链表相对于数组, 最大的优势就是删除和增加操作, 数组需要平移操作, 但是链表只需要改指针, 链表的删除增加操作, 时间复杂度是 O(1), 但是链表除了<code class=\"language-text\">head</code>和<code class=\"language-text\">tail</code>可以直接访问外, 链表节点的访问必须遍历节点, 时间复杂度是 O(n) , 链表和数组各有利弊.</p>\n<h2>跳表</h2>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/6569d/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 39.189189189189186%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"跳表\"\n        title=\"跳表\"\n        src=\"/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/fcda8/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/12f09/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 148w,\n/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/e4a3f/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 295w,\n/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/fcda8/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 590w,\n/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/efc66/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 885w,\n/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/c83ae/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 1180w,\n/static/dfb4e7134aba0aa54b17a8196965bcd6/6569d/%E8%B7%B3%E8%A1%A8.png 1328w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>通过升维, 携带多级索引的链表就是跳表.</p>\n<p>跳表有个前提, 就是原始链表必须是有序的.</p>\n<p>因为多携带了索引信息, 所以跳表占用内存比链表大, 但是跳表的查询时间复杂度是 O(logn), 比链表的 O(n)快得多.</p>\n<p>跳表的查询过程:</p>\n<p>如上图, 我们要查询 10,</p>\n<ol>\n<li>从第二级索引开始遍历, 1 -> 7 , 发现 7 小于 10, 从 1 的索引向一级索引遍历, 遍历了 2 个节点</li>\n<li>第一级索引, 7 -> 9 , 发现 9 小于 10, 从 9 的索引向原始链表遍历, 遍历了 1 个节点</li>\n<li>原始链表, 9 -> 10, 找到目标元素, 遍历了 1 个节点</li>\n</ol>\n<p>一共遍历了 4 个节点, 相比原始链表直接遍历 8 个节点效率上有所提升.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"数据结构-数组、链表、跳表基本特性","date":"2020/08/12","description":null,"tags":["leetcode"]}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/数据结构-数组、链表、跳表基本实现和特性/数据结构-数组、链表、跳表基本实现和特性/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/CSS函数/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS函数"}},"next":null}}}